data.description: Welcome to this quiet 3 bed, 2 bath homestead less than a mile from Sequoyah State Park and Ft. Gibson Lake!  Inside, the kitchen features a vaulted ceiling, island with electric, a large pantry and freshly painted white cabinets.  The living room has a wood burning stove.  The 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths can be shut-off from the living area and all bedrooms have walk-in closets with built in shelving! The 2 acres m/l was recently fully fenced and gated which can be split into 3 separate areas.  The 2-car garage is attached to the home by a breezeway.  New roof on home and garage in 2022.  A 1,000 gallon rain water collection system will provide plenty of fresh water for your animals and plants or a backup for you.  There is a sizable tilled garden area, covered front porch and the home is off of a paved road.  Don't let this opportunity slip away!
